{"tid":1689231,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"消防處正式成為 警務處 - 消防部","createTime":"2019-11-02T17:18:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T17:39:07.000Z","uid":2719,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4a8f22dd714520bef91e1f63dbe074c7b9c46f97","tid":1689231,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:18:48.000Z","msg":"1. 開閘救人 ( 俾狗屌 )<br />\n2. 休班消防 ( 俾休班狗指住屌 )<br />\n3. 消防車中彈 ( 無視 )<br />\n4. 消防員俾狗圍 ( 無視 )<br />\n5. 消防車運狗 ( 俾狗佔用 )<br />\n6. 消防俾狗調動 ( 跟班，聽令救火/即救中火魔法狗 )<br />\n7. 狗話消防數錯831太子傷者人數 ( 狗直接話消防無能 )<br />\n8. 狗阻止消防救援工作 ( 狗俾放行先可救 )<br />\n<br />\n以上全部針對消防高層，前線唔好代號入座。<br />\n但高層就係代表消防處，你地前線只係執行，<br />\n依家高層跪要你地聽命於狗，你地就係狗嘅支分部。<br />\n<br />\n係唔岩聽，但現實就係由依家開始，再無消防處，<br />\n只有「警務處 - 消防部」"},{"pid":"f1b6e94438bdbab8a31545f39ad040439797a9f1","tid":1689231,"uid":262146,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:19:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/daWoJsy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdaWoJsy.png&h=16518c90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oLQwSkW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoLQwSkW.png&h=766c26b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TLR4sUj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTLR4sUj.png&h=1dd0aacc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n死黑警從來無認真關心過香港人條命<br />\n講緊被死亡個案，佢仲係度冷笑、當笑話"},{"pid":"ef3bf8d8f3c764b88a67ee6bdfac5ea54d9bb6ee","tid":1689231,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T17:20:08.000Z","msg":"催淚彈疑撃中消防車消防員不滿 與警員理論時反被包圍 - RTHK <br />\n(記者再再再再次被針對及阻礙採訪)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/ceb12\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fceb12&d=5AUjfk%2BhgFT%2FKzSacqcGpBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=4e571fa7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/ceb12</a><br />\n<br />\n開槍射消防<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\